headline: SLB Capturi powers up its first modular carbon capture plant
summary: OSLO, Norway, January 23, 2025--Global energy technology company SLB (NYSE: SLB) announced today that SLB Capturi has completed commissioning and is handing over its modular carbon capture plant at Twence’s waste-to-energy facility in Hengelo, Netherlands.
